The Matrix Arcade

This is the ultimate collection of The Matrix flash games which includes all six of the official web games that were freely available on The Matrix official website before it went offline in late 2008. Also included is twenty of the very best unofficial flash games having The Matrix theme as well as a real cool handful of The Matrix related flash animated short films.

These games are played within your favorite web browser such as Internet Explorer or Firefox without having to install any additional software and also without having to be online or connected to the internet. This is accomplished by associating your browser with the games.
